"overall_meaning": "Then Prajapati said, 'Who is that person seen in the eye?  He is the Self. This is immortal, fearless, this is Brahman.'  Then he said, 'Who is this Lord reflected in the water, and who is this in the mirror? This indeed is reflected in all arrow tips.' "
